title: Shaun Micallef's Mad As Hell S05E03.mp4
description:
Here (by request) is Episode 3 Series 5 of Shaun Micallef's Mad As Hell - his latest extremely witty and hilarious sojourn into political satire and general funniness. The show features an excellent support cast of well known Australian comedians.

This file is a bit more compressed than the last two. I took it down a few notches for the video kbps to keep the weight down. Video = x264@1200kbps, Audio = AAC@192kbps. The economy is hardly noticeable on the final file but everyone will get it a little quicker.

Screen resolution is fine, high quality SD at 720x404.

I have some pretty extreme limitations about my internet supply at the moment so I'll only be able to upload these ep's for a couple of hours a night (between 7pm and 9pm AET). Sorry if you don't get it all in one whack, but I can only do what I can (in very limited ways) for the time being. Once the first peers have got full episodes, if they could continue to seed, eventually everyone who wants it will have it. I'll also look into seedboxing them so they'll be a bit stronger to begin with.

So, in the true Aussie spirit, be cool and gimme a hand when you're finished downloading.

Cheers,
MoofieMan
